    "ItemDescription": {
      "Namespace": "",
      "Key": "7A6C160240F673601A4959A59AD8BE3B",
      "SourceString": "Add to a weapon's Relic Slot while crafting to deal ELEMENTAL EARTH damage and use the Tecto-Tunneling ability. Strong against LIGHTNING.\n\nDeal more ELEMENTAL EARTH Damage.\n\nTecto-tunneling - Charge your weapon by dealing damage. When fully charged, use <keybind touch_img=\"TectoTunneling\">Target</> to swiftly tunnel into the EARTH. Attack while underground to explode to the surface and deal ELEMENTAL EARTH damage, before diving back into the ground.",
